</span></font></code>
It specifies the accuracy with which
to approximate the exponential function value; i.e.,
it is the value of 
<math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mrow>
<mi mathvariant='normal'>&#x003B5;</mi>
</mrow></math>

